# ==============================================================================
# .dockerignore
# PURPOSE: Zero-Leakage Build Context Shield
# ==============================================================================

# 1. Block Private Data and Credentials (CRITICAL)
.private-vault/
**/.env
**/.env.deploy
**/.env.local
mcp-config.json

# 2. Block Local State and Logs
**/node_modules
**/npm-debug.log*
**/.DS_Store

# 3. Block Version Control
.git/
.gitignore

# 4. Block Development Documentation
docs/internal/
GEMINI.md
PUBLIC_GOODS_OPEN_SOURCE_HANDBOOK.md
